rows.label: tlk43100341_01_msg0001
rows.name:
My younger brother
Veero's such a crybaby.

rows.label: tlk43100341_01_msg0002
rows.name:
This one time, he tripped and skinned
his knee the tiniest bit, but he was
bawling about it for hours!

rows.label: tlk43100341_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I don't see how he's going to handle
being an Invidian soldier...

rows.label: tlk43100341_01_msg0004
rows.name:
The only thing he's good at
is studying, really. I'm kind
of worried about him...
